FUTURE ROADMAP:

Zero Mode - mask: TR-0000
TR-0000 - initialized with 0
TR-0001
TR-0011
TR-0111
TR-1111

Number Mode - mask: NNNNNNNN
      0 - initialized with 0
      1
     10
    100
  1.000
 10.000
100.000

Currency mode - mask: R$ CCCCCCCCCC
     R$ 0,00 - initialized with 0
     R$ 0,05 - first type
     R$ 0,55
     R$ 5,55
    R$ 55,55
   R$ 555,55
 R$ 5.555,55
R$ 55.555,55
